title: Human Events Daily - Oct 12 2021 - The #FREEDOMFLU Special
description:
Many of you saw, over the weekend we got #FreedomFlu trending across social media. In this episode of Human Events, Jack breaks down the multi-faceted fronts of the Freedom Flu, and how it is affecting every aspect of life, from food supplies to air travel. 


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
